  },
  {
    icon: '⚡',
    title: 'Captures Recommendation-Driven Leads',
    text: "Tree surgery businesses thrive on recommendations — 'used these guys for our oak, brilliant work' tagged on a local Facebook group. The recommendation drives a follower to your page, they message, and the AI captures the enquiry within seconds."
